==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tubby
<hw>Tub"by</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Resembling a tub;
specifically sounding dull and without resonance, like a tub; wanting
elasticity or freedom of sound; <as>as, a <ex>tubby</ex>
violin</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tube</ent>⟦br⟧
